'''磷酸钪'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为ScPO<sub>4</sub>，它是[[四方晶系|四方晶系]]的晶体，可由[[氧化钪|氧化钪]]和稀[[磷酸|磷酸]]在400 °C进行水热反应得到。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica|volume=9|issue=8|issn=0365-110X|date=1956-08-01|pages=677–678|doi=10.1107/S0365110X56001807|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0365110X56001807|title=The structure of anhydrous scandium phosphate|accessdate=2020-10-31|author=R. C. L. Mooney|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602015124/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0365110X56001807|dead-url=no}}</ref>磷酸或其钠盐和钪盐反应，可以沉淀出六方晶系的ScPO<sub>4</sub>·2H<sub>2</sub>O。<ref>Komissarova, L. N.; Mel'nikov, P. P.; Kravtsova, R. P.; Spitsyn, V. I. Preparation and properties of crystalline scandium orthophosphate dihydrate. ''Zeitschrift für Chemie'', 1965. 5 (11): 429-430. ISSN: 0044-2402. CODEN: ZECEAL.</ref>磷酸钪和[[磷酸银|磷酸银]]在高温反应，可以得到Ag<sub>3</sub>Sc(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Less Common Metals|volume=99|issue=2|language=en|date=1984-06|pages=L25–L26|doi=10.1016/0022-5088(84)90236-4|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022508884902364|title=Silver scandium double phosphate|accessdate=2020-10-31|author=P.P. Melnikov, J.D.Carrillo Heredero, L.N. Komissarova|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603051933/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022508884902364|dead-url=no}}</ref>

